00:06:03.759 --> 00:06:08.300
Jessie wakes up from her sleep. And her whole
body is in pain, due to the irregular circulation

00:06:08.300 --> 00:06:12.900
of blood in her body, She starts to scream
in pain. After a few minutes of screaming,

00:06:12.900 --> 00:06:17.499
She grabs the water and starts drinking it.
Imaginary Gerald asks her why she didn’t

00:06:17.499 --> 00:06:22.270
tell him about her father. Jessie had told
no one about what happened with her father.

00:06:22.270 --> 00:06:26.229
Imaginary Jessie tells her that she married
a man just like her father. Jessie starts

00:06:26.229 --> 00:06:30.870
crying, and Gerald reminds her about the tall
figure she had seen last night. He shows her

00:06:30.870 --> 00:06:34.960
the footprint on the floor. He tells her that
the tall figure was real, and that it will

00:06:34.960 --> 00:06:36.400
come again tonight.

00:06:36.400 --> 00:06:40.530
In the past, Jessie’s father comes to her
