And Jessie also promises that she will not

00:06:49.660 --> 00:06:50.860
tell anyone.

00:06:50.860 --> 00:06:55.729
At present time, the stray dog is still taking
bites off Gerald’s body. Gerald asks Jessie

00:06:55.729 --> 00:07:00.180
what will happen to her after she dies. He
tells her that when people find their body,

00:07:00.180 --> 00:07:04.010
