00:07:25.020 --> 00:07:29.819
She grabs the glass and breaks it. With the
broken piece of glass, Jessie cuts her wrist.

00:07:29.819 --> 00:07:33.529
She knew that the blood was slippery. She
uses the blood and finally gets her hand out

00:07:33.529 --> 00:07:38.250
